PACKAGES AND CLASS DESCRIPTION:
main.ScrapingComponents.Ingredients:  this class contains reusable components
scrapesoups.ClientSoup.ClientSoup: this class contains actual code for soups
scrapesoups.LinkExtract.LinkExtract: This class is for extracting links
scrapesoups.DataExtract.DataExtract: This class is for extracting data form links

Ingredients:
__init__(self,_driver) - constructor takes the driver parameter
scrollPageDown(self) - scrolls down a web page till the end
getOutputFilesPath() - returns the path of the output folder for cancatinating with filename for writing outputs
writeToFileWithSeperators(filename,list[]) - used to write ouput data with seperators. field seperator - '|^|', link seperator - '|!|' 
writeToFile(filename,url) - write a single link to file
writeListToFile(filename,urls[]) - write a list to file with '\n'
